pages-strings.Find what you're looking for in our deta:
Find what you're looking for in our detailed documentation and guides.

- Learn how to [get started](/metro-bundler/docs/en/getting-started.html) with Metro.
- [Troubleshoot](/metro-bundler/docs/en/troubleshooting.html) problems with Metro.
- Learn how to [configure Metro](/metro-bundler/docs/en/configuration.html).
- Look at the full [API Reference](/metro-bundler/docs/en/api.html).
pages-strings.Ask questions and find answers from othe:
Ask questions and find answers from other Metro users like you.

- Join the [#metro](https://discordapp.com/channels/102860784329052160/103622435865104384) channel on [Reactiflux](http://www.reactiflux.com/), a Discord community.
- Many members of the community use Stack Overflow. Read through the [existing questions](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/metrojs) tagged with **metrojs** or [ask your own](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/ask)!
pages-strings.Find out what's new with Metro.\\n\\n- F:
Find out what's new with Metro.

- Follow [Metro](https://twitter.com/MetroBundler) on Twitter.
- Subscribe to the [Metro blog](/metro-bundler/blog/).
pages-strings.Metro Bundler is worked on full-time by: Metro Bundler is worked on full-time by Facebook's JavaScript Foundation team. Team members are often around and available for questions.
pages-strings.Metro aims for sub-second reload cycles,: Metro aims for sub-second reload cycles, fast startup and quick bundling speeds.
pages-strings.Works with thousands of modules in a sin: Works with thousands of modules in a single application.
pages-strings.Supports every React Native project out: Supports every React Native project out of the box.
